edu.hm.cs.se.game.app

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.hm.cs.se.game.app.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for all types of fields: game fields and player fields. A field may contain a pawn. A field can be assigned to a special player.
